title: Account transfer NA to OCE
body: Hi, I just wanted to ask if it could take much longer to complete the process of account transferring from NA to OCE.. I bought rp to move my account to Oce server an hour ago.  I can be patient as it could take up to 24 hours.

replies.body: I checked up on your transfer status, and it looks like you're now on the OCE server! Hit us back up if you're not able to login to the OCE server still.
